### Orders API Tests
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api/v1

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = YOUR_TOKEN
@adminToken = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN
@orderId = YOUR_ORDER_ID

### Create Order
POST {{baseUrl}}/orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "Amara Okafor",
  "customerEmail": "amara.okafor@email.com",
  "items": [
    { "productId": "YOUR_PRODUCT_ID", "quantity": 1 }
  ],
  "shippingAddress": "15 Admiralty Way, Lekki Phase 1",
  "city": "Lagos",
  "postalCode": "101245",
  "country": "Nigeria"
}

### My Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/my-orders
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Request Refund
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/request-refund
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refundReason": "Size does not fit as expected"
}

### Update Order Status (Admin)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/orders/{{orderId}}/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Shipped"
}

### Admin - Get All Orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/orders/admin/all
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
